BrightBlade, Rage

* BrightBlade patted the ground beside her as she finished a grape, she had 
nearly eaten half the bushel Gangon had plucked down but she had saved the 
rest for him.
She smiled*

" Come on, sit."

^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

* Rage growled at the battle about her, she had seen Scourge run off and 
kick Set but she didn't know what to do.
Was she to attack, and is so then who?
She hadn't met all of the members of Scourge's team and she might end up 
killing or even eating a member. Then she would be in big trouble!
Rage looked around but spotted no real bots that seemed to her liking or 
taste, she then began to sniff the air. Wait!
Her stomach rumbled, she smelled fowl!
Rage looed around but saw nothing that matched the scent, she then put her 
snout to the wind and began to follow it.
She stretched her body up so that she could get a better reading on the 
smell, it was coming from the bushes!
Rage snapped her head towards where she thought that she smelled some sort 
of bird, her stomach growled again.
Perhaps it was her lucky day after all!*
